<|channel>thought
<channel|># 副簽
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺主要簽署人簽名之後，由另一個人喺旁邊簽名以示認可或確認（量詞：個）
eng:countersign / cosign
<eg>
yue:呢份文件除咗經理簽名，仲需要由部門主管副簽先至有效。 (ni1 fan6 man4 gin2 ceoi4 zo2 ging1 lei2 cim1 ming4, zung6 seoi1 jau4 jau4 bo1 mun4 zyu2 gun2 fu3 cim1 sin1 zi3 jau5 haau6.)
eng:This document needs to be countersigned by the department head in addition to the manager's signature to be valid. [end of text]


